 our views of human evolution and human nature.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aChromosome X. 0aGenetic sex determination. 0aSex determination, Genetic. 0aSexexDétermination génétique. 0aX chromosome. 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Biology.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/9780674020412zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674020412423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674020412/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK